# Demo media in gif/ (Dashboard.mp4 ~27 MB, Evidence-First AI Research.gif
# ~18.5 MB) are both under GitHub's 100 MB per-file push limit, so a normal
# `git push` works — Git LFS is optional.
#
# If you'd rather keep them out of regular history, uncomment the lines below
# and run `git lfs install` once before committing.
# *.gif  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
# *.mp4  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
# *.mov  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
# *.webm filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text

# Treat media as binary (no line-ending/diff noise).
*.gif  binary
*.mp4  binary
*.mov  binary
*.webm binary
